.UNINDENT
.sp
Configure how the C Driver reports errors. See Setting the Error API Version\&.
.SH PARAMETERS
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBpool\fP: A \fBmongoc_client_pool_t\fP\&.
.IP \(bu 2
